    "description": "沉浸在门户物理世界中激动人心的冒险中！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/03a5422ef43d4fae12bede1d29e523df.poster.avif?t=1729703340\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/03a5422ef43d4fae12bede1d29e523df.webm?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/03a5422ef43d4fae12bede1d29e523df.mp4?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这款 3D 平台游戏中，您必须使用传送枪解决谜题，克服障碍并前进。探索奇异的地点，激活机制，并通过巧妙地使用门户，打开通往新关卡的道路。<br><br>面对需要逻辑和灵活性的挑战，穿过扭曲的迷宫到达终点线。每个新的阶段都会给你带来更多的谜题和展示你技能的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/bf7da7f0d33e7976c652e84f0ca993a0.poster.avif?t=1729703340\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/bf7da7f0d33e7976c652e84f0ca993a0.webm?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/bf7da7f0d33e7976c652e84f0ca993a0.mp4?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>让自己沉浸在激动人心的游戏中，门户物理将成为你获胜的关键。通过解决谜题来挑战自己，发现非凡的新世界！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/7869b03812e685392099baaa183948a0.poster.avif?t=1729703340\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/7869b03812e685392099baaa183948a0.webm?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as